<br>
Slam - Anytime - 9 Seconds<br>
Stunning Blow/Devastating Blow - After Parry - 10 Seconds<br>
Brutalize - After Block - 12 Seconds<br>
(If you go 50 shield)<br>
<br>
Because, at this point, you have so many stun styles, and only being able to use one every minute due to resistance timers, in one manner of speaking makes them pointless, and in another manner, makes it so you can potentially have a stun no matter what melee your opponent throws your way, if you do happen to parry or block them, and you'll get a better stun off. Of course, you still have the rest of the Blunt line to consider in terms of effectiveness, which is by no means shabby.<br>
<br>
*IF* you were to go a pierce spec, you would have no after-parry styles to be concerned about, and you could really utilize a full 50 shield for after-block 12 second stun. Also, attacking fast with a piercer like that makes reactionary-styles for your opponent harder to do too <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Another thing to keep in mind is Blademasters and not having Mastery of Blocking to spec into. That is one of the biggest things holding me back from speccing Shield currently, from a defensive (Offensive considering Brutalize) standpoint. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=120.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=120.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=120.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=120.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.threadControl?topicID=120.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=120.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=120.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" vali